## Student Dashboard

### Dashboard Overview
The Student Dashboard provides students with tools to browse thesis projects, submit applications, manage assessments, and track their academic progress.

### Main Dashboard Components

#### Project Discovery Panel
- **Available Projects**: Browse open thesis projects
- **Search and Filter**: Find projects by type, topic, or supervisor
- **Project Details**: Comprehensive project information
- **Quick Apply**: Direct application to projects

#### Application Management
- **My Applications**: Track application status
- **Application History**: View all submitted applications
- **Status Updates**: Real-time application status
